data.description: Beautiful contemporary home on 1.8+/- acres in Forest Park.This home has been completely rebuilt just over 2 years ago due to a house fire. Many updates including all new electrical, plumbing, new kitchen with quartz counters, baths with granite, birch wood flooring & ceramic tile in baths upstairs, durable vinyl plank flooring downstairs. The open concept floor plan is stunning w/cathedral ceilings, gas log ready double-sided fireplace between the dining and living area. A first floor laundry is located in the foyer. Not only do you have a main floor primary suite which has been expanded to provide a luxurious space, you also have a second primary suite downstairs! 3 additional bedrooms, 1 on the main floor and 2 downstairs with one having access to the full hall bath. Continued........ Also downstairs is the family room w/wood burning fireplace insert, second laundry, kitchenette and storage room. On the back of the home is a large deck for entertaining w/patio and screened storage area underneath.
